import Data from './Data.json'
import { useState } from "react"
const App = () => {
  const [state, setState] = useState(Data)
  return (
    <>
     
      {state.map((list) => {
        return (
          <>
          <img src={list.pic} alt="" width="300px"/>
          <p>{list.name}</p>
          </>
        )
        
      })}
 
    </>
  )
}
export default App
